# Accepted findings, one per line, with rationale. Anything not listed here
# (or inline-ignored at the resource with a justification) fails the gate.

# Kubernetes probes (readiness/liveness in the chart) are the health
# mechanism; Docker HEALTHCHECK is redundant in-cluster and impossible in a
# distroless image (no shell to run a check with).
AVD-DS-0026

# Chart templates intentionally omit metadata.namespace — Helm assigns the
# release namespace (installed with -n hello-world --create-namespace).
AVD-KSV-0110

# CPU limits are deliberately unset: CPU is compressible and hard limits
# cause throttling; the chart sets CPU requests + memory limits instead.
AVD-KSV-0011

# GHCR is our registry of record (images built and pushed by this repo's CI,
# deployed by immutable sha- tag); it's not in Trivy's default trusted list.
AVD-KSV-0125
